  "instructions": [
    "heat the chicken broth in a large clay pot or tandoor over medium heat until it starts to simmer.",
    "add the chopped onion and saut\u00071 it until it's translucent.",
    "add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "add the collard greens, red pepper flakes, paprika, cumin, salt, and black pepper.",
    "stir to combine, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes, or until the greens are tender.",
    "use an immersion blender to blend the soup until it's smooth.",
    "stir in the heavy cream and cook over low heat until warmed through.",
    "taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "garnish with chopped cilantro before serving.",
